text: Yalli malaykay seehadayti dacayrih sittal ciggilta le, is Yallih amrih umaane celli haytaamak foocaa kee derrek kaa dacrissa;diggah Yalli seehadah yecee niqmat keenik ma seelabaay keenik makorsa, usun sinni nafsih Yalli ken kah amrise meqe taama cabbaay uma taamah abitt√¥ fanah gacca iyyaanam fanah, Yalli sinaamal digaalah bala oobisam faxek, toysa tet keenik gacissaah waasam matan, usun Yallak kalah awlaytuy keenil obta bala keenik waasaah keenik cata malon
